data.description: From the moment you step onto this Luxury Estate you will be impressed.  The large circular driveway provides plenty of space for your guests to park.  Everyone will be awed by the beautiful grounds leading to the home.  The landscaping throughout the property is breathtaking.    Enter this Luxury Custom-Built home and you are greeted by a large luxury entry foyer.  Adjacent is a Formal Dining room, large enough to accommodate even the most discerning host and all the guests.    The very large living room, with an amazing fireplace creates an entertainer’s haven. Complete with a custom-built bar and lounge space.  The floor to ceiling windows and doors open to the most magnificent view of the huge tropical backyard.  The remodeled kitchen is a chef’s delight with beautiful cabinetry and granite counter tops.  There is another large dining area off the kitchen for casual dining.  If that isn’t enough, the Living Room and Kitchen open to a large deck which extends throughout the back of the home.  There is a custom-built outdoor grill on the deck for dining alfresco.  And of course, plenty of outdoor living space.    The Master Suite includes the master bedroom, luxury master bathroom, its own living room and private office with built in office cabinetry.  This is a great Retreat when the home is bustling with overnight guests or family sleepovers.  There are 4 other sizeable bedrooms and 2 other bathrooms and plenty of storage throughout the home.  The floorplan is a split floorplan so there is plenty of separation for everyone’s privacy.    The home even has a Mud Room leading from the oversized 3 car garage. Where do you see that in Florida?  And the laundry room is very large with additional storage.    This home sits on a very large private lot.  Curlew creek runs below and behind the property, and this affords a great deal of privacy. In fact, you don’t even see the neighbors’ homes behind the home.  The backyard is magnificent, like  your own city park.  You will feel like you are walking in the country.  There is a storage room built under the deck for added backyard storage.  The yard is so large you can build any form of entertainment the heart desires, pool, tennis court, pickle ball, etc.    Additional amenities include: A deep water well to supply the home and the irrigation system. An owned security alarm system along with intercom, ring doorbell, and security cameras.  Roof is only 3 years old. New AC 2021 and the decking was upgraded.    There is so much included in the property – you just have to see it.      Conveniently located to Downtown Dunedin and all its bars, restaurants, shops, and festivals. Honeymoon Island and the Ferry to Caladesi Island are one mile close.  Or a quick jump onto US 19 and you will be minutes from Clearwater, Tampa, and St. Petersburg.      It is hard to find a FINE LUXURY HOME this close to City & Beaches!    Buyer to verify measurements.
